      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">7/7/88 ¶ Best thanks for the  ¶ Achnophora ¶ , esteemed Mr Tepper, ¶  the other plant enclosed is  ¶ Lagenophora billardierii ¶ .  ¶ However, I see no second unnamed plant from Kangaroo Island ¶  with...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">88.07.07b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">7/7/88</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Besten Dank für die <name key="Achnophora">Achnophora</name>, geehrter Herr Tepper, die beigefügte andre Pflanze ist Lagenophora Billardierii. Ich sehe aber keine zweite unbenannte Pflanze aus der Känguruh Insel dabei. Die Auszeichnung von Greiz haben Sie ehrenhaft verdiendt, u entbiete ich Ihnen meinen besten Glückwunsch.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie ehrend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Sie haben ganz recht in dem, welches Sie über Anerkennung im eignen Lande sagen. Der grösste Planzenkenner hier, der mit deren </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Erfordernissen</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> in Culturen durch ein halbes Jahrhundert vertraut ist, darf noch </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">nicht einen</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Acker Grund aus den Tausenden Ackern offentl. Gartenlands hier bei der Stadt für sich haben!</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">7/7/88</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Best thanks for the </seg>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Achnophora">Achnophora</name>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">, esteemed Mr Tepper,</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Requested in M to O. Tepper, 2 July 1888, which is annotated by Tepper noting that the specimen was sent on 4 July 1888; no letter of that date by Tepper to M has been found. See also M to O. Tepper 28 July 1888.</p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> the other plant enclosed is </seg>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Lagenophora%20billardierii">Lagenophora billardierii</name>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">. </seg>However, I see no second unnamed plant from Kangaroo Island<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>SA.</p>
               </note> with it. You have honourably deserved the distinction of patriarch, and I offer my best wishes to you.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">You are quite right in what you say about recognition in your own country. The greatest plant specialist here, who is well acquainted with its <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">requirements</hi>
               </seg> in cultivation for half a century, is <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">not</hi>
               </seg> yet permitted to have <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">one</hi>
               </seg> acre of ground from the thousands of acres of public gardens here in the city for himself.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Achnophora">Achnophora</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Lagenophora%20billardierii">Lagenophora billardierii</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
